// # 🍔 BiteStream - Food Reel Sharing Platform

// BiteStream is a full-stack MERN (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js) application designed for food enthusiasts to discover and share culinary inspiration through short-form video reels.

// The platform features a dual-user ecosystem where general users can browse a dynamic feed of food content, while authenticated creators have the power to upload and manage their own reels.

// ## 🚀 Features

// - **Dynamic Video Feed:** Seamlessly scroll through a curated collection of food reels.
// - **Dual-Role System:** - **Viewers:** Can browse, view, and interact with the food feed.
//   - **Creators (Auth):** Access to a private dashboard to upload, edit, and delete their video content.
// - **Secure Authentication:** Implemented using **JWT (JSON Web Tokens)** and **bcrypt** for secure password hashing.
// - **Role-Based Access Control (RBAC):** Middleware-protected routes ensure only authorized users can manage content.
// - **Responsive Design:** Optimized for a smooth viewing experience across mobile, tablet, and desktop devices.

// ## 🛠️ Tech Stack

// **Frontend:**
// - React.js
// - Tailwind CSS (or CSS Modules)
// - Axios for API communication
// - React Router for navigation

// **Backend:**
// - Node.js & Express.js
// - MongoDB & Mongoose (ODM)
// - JWT for secure authorization
// - Multer/Cloudinary (for video storage handling)

